    80→            </span>
    81→          </div>
    82→          <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    83→            This code will expire in 15 minutes. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
    84→          </p>
    85→        </div>
    86→      `,
    87→      text: `Your verification code is: ${code}. It will expire in 15 minutes.`,
    88→    });
    89→  }
